{
  "stem": "11175.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I'm talking about the ghetto, how they closed up the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the people that was in the ghetto and not having every day, every single day we had funerals, and funerals.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Moshe's died.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They had died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They had died.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had funerals constantly there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We had to take them out.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And the ghetto was-- they started in 1942-- the liquidation from that ghetto started in 1942.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "They came in and we heard-- you know, some other places-- from some other places for how they-- they are handling everything that they can get together-- the people, they took them out to the trains, to the cattle cars.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And this was an early morning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "In a fall-- September.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Before the holidays.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "This was somewhere around September.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "We heard the ghettos full with-- you know-- with Germans.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And Ukrainians came into the ghetto, and started to take out people.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And they made there like a little Umschlagplatz right by this station there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And they--they fooled them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They said, you're going to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They asked the women to take some-- some powder, some salt, because you're going to wash the clothing.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And everybody grabbed for whatever they can and then they went out, you see.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they took them over to that place where they have the-- they took them together at that station, in the [NON-ENGLISH] station.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And they start to load them up to the-- I was remaining in that ghetto.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I was there in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "I was hiding myself.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And the-- the woman what I was with her, she was in a separate, but I didn't know where she is.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And she didn't know where I am.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Finally, we found ourselves.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And the child was with her parents.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
